        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
            "1. From the previous chain from al-Hassan from Abi al-Maghraa’ from ’Anbasa b. Mus’ab from Abi Abdillah (a.s.) who said: “One who recites Surah Ibrahim and Surah Hijr in two rakats on Friday would never get involved in poverty, insanity and calamity.”"
